# 🧠 ROOT CAUSE

DNS resolution failure caused by incorrect or invalid nameserver configuration in `/etc/resolv.conf`.

---

# 🟢 PHASE 5 — RESOLUTION

---

### 🔹 Step 9 — Fix DNS

```bash
sudo vi /etc/resolv.conf
```

Replace with:

```
nameserver 8.8.8.8
```

---

